name: Heat bagged
description:
My Garmin (which sits between my hands all day) reported a maximum temperature of 41C.

We were aiming for Sicamous, but it's too hot to keep going so we stopped for dinner in Grindrod, and will be camping here. 

My left knee is still bothering me. I'll need a rest day soon to let my legs recover. We're looking forward to a day with no climbing soon.
